CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Bowlero Corp is a operator of bowling entertainment centers. It operate traditional bowling centers and more upscale entertainment concepts with lounge seating, arcades, enhanced food and beverage offerings, and more robust customer service for individuals and group events, as well as hosting and overseeing professional and non-professional bowling tournaments and related broadcasting.
